          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The recoiling alpha-particles were detected by",
                "an array of six standard silicon surface barrier",
                "detectors, each separated by 6 degree and mounted on a",
                "turntable. A fixed detector at -15 degree was used for",
                "monitoring and for normalization of the angular",
                "settings. The seven detectors varied in thickness",
                " 1.5-5 mm and in area 50-200 mm**2. The time of flight",
                "was measured in the experiment using the cyclotron RF",
                "signal and the fast signal from the Si detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
